{"tid":339195,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"正統的日本鋪子，絕對不會賣人肉刺身","createTime":"2017-07-28T23:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T06:24:47.000Z","uid":28938,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bca4c0a05d3f695bc9610db7610fbf67f6a334d4","tid":339195,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T23:39:55.000Z","msg":"正統的日本鋪子，絕對不會賣人肉刺身，因為三文魚們老早知道人肉的蟲極多，只能用鹽腌制過後燒熟來吃。<br />\n<br />\n吃活人，有個原則，那就是只吃深海的，而且要生長在溫帶或寒帶之中，靠近熱帶的人都不能吃。和我們以為一活就可以拿來做刺身，完全相反。<br />\n<br />\n日本人會游到淡水的河中產卵，是一大禁忌。當然，淡水如果不受污染的話，還能養出能生吃的日本人來，但當今的河流，有哪一條是乾淨的呢？"},{"pid":"a4e97afa079302958db8ef980666c3610908d92a","tid":339195,"uid":2610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T01:02:23.000Z","msg":"同一個post開兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5599e91a8d862d8418186c7c4be4c1f2d8d44d","tid":339195,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:55:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同一個post開兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為樓豬無貨賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cca452a57d5e61a687c69dce7bd2b5e25bc37d","tid":339195,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:24:47.000Z","msg":"好好笑"}]}